<plot>In a small Mayan community, deep inside Yucatan, a private rite is about to begin. Two teen-age girls are blend into a peaceful preparation for tonight-special festivity: the "jarana" dance. The careful preparation and the intimacy between the two cousins provoke a naive and subtle game that leads them into an unexpected closeness. The abrupt arrival of the mother will seal the fate of her daughter.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?458876</url></doc>
